						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the market place.</p>						

						<p>Vikramāditya VI [1081].</p>						

						<p>The upper portion of the stone is badly damaged. It dated Chālukya-Vikrama year 4, Siddhārthi, Kārttika śu 5, Sunday. The details are not regular.</p>						

						<p>Seems to record a gift by a <hi rend="italic">Mahāsāmanta</hi> (details lost).</p>						

